FBIS4-60788 "drsov084_m_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-084 Daily Report 29 Apr 1994 Tajikistan Deputy Premier, Broadcasting Chief Appointed Deputy Premier, Broadcasting Chief Appointed LD2904162894 Moscow RIA in English 0827 GMT 29 Apr 94 LD2904162894 Moscow RIA English BFN [Text] Dushanbe, April 29, RIA -- The Presidium of the Supreme Soviet of Tajikistan appointed Bozgul Dodkhudoyeva, former minister of education, to the post of deputy chairperson of the Cabinet of Ministers. Izbraghim Usmanov, secretary of the Central Committee of the Tajik Communist Party, was appointed to the post of chairman of the State Committee on Radio and Television.
